students.name: Student 1
students.description: With her perpetually ink-stained fingers and a cascade of fiery red hair, devoured ancient texts and star charts with equal fervor.  Her notebook, a chaotic mix of arcane symbols and complex equations, hinted at a mind constantly weaving connections between forgotten lore and the cosmos.  She often spoke in riddles, her eyes sparkling with an otherworldly curiosity.
